lead_paragraph: Park In-bee suffered the disappointment of seeing her incredible bogey-free streak come to an end after 115 holes but the Korean opened her HSBC Women's Champions title defense with a solid first round to sit just one shot off the lead on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Park Poised in Singapore Despite End to Incredible Streak
